        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer562396056" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16417093879100409687">An American Rabbi explores the Korean War through the eyes of an old couple and a young orphan. You wouldn&apos;t think that it would work, but I thought that it was first rate. I thought that you&apos;d struggle to find a bleaker work than The Road, but this hits you harder because the journey is so depressingly plausible. Not for the faint-hearted. A-.</span>
  <span id="freeText16417093879100409687" style="display:none">An American Rabbi explores the Korean War through the eyes of an old couple and a young orphan. You wouldn't think that it would work, but I thought that it was first rate. I thought that you'd struggle to find a bleaker work than The Road, but this hits you harder because the journey is so depressingly plausible. Not for the faint-hearted. A-.</span>
